AMTS Routes is a simple application that is aimed for people who travel using AMTS. The application allows user to view 
route of buses using their bus nos, users can search a bus that will take you from a source to a destination. Users can 
also view list of buses that go to a specific stop.

AMTS Routes is a voluntary application, and is not an official AMTS apps. The routes are updated as per best of our
knowledge. If you find that any bus details or bus stops that are missing, then you can update us about them using the 
feedback functionality.

We hope that you'll like this app and it will helpful in your day to day life.
